name: Crypto Bro
description: This is the story of a young boy, who was not very popular or liked, but he just wanted to be the coolest most popular kid ever. His friends all grew up and became moderately successful, and bought houses and cars. But he was just a loser. This is the story of a young boy, who was not very popular or liked, but he just wanted to be the coolest most popular kid ever. Every day, as he jerked off while playing world of warcraft, his desire to be successful would grow. Little did he know that luck was afoot.
